Package: PitchMendR
Title: Fix Pitch Tracking Errors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Sostarics", , "tsostarics@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1178-7967"))
Description: This package provides an interface to modify pitch samples saved in a csv file. Users can remove spurious tracking errors and non-destructively fix halving/doubling errors.
